    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/73d64495abce54f457dc219698e0e1b4.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用能量球的力量点燃火炬并完成关卡。但即使有它们的帮忙也挑战十足：你需要精准准确而及时的瞄准，发射！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/58d8aa807cc486f14ce4eb7475d9e08e.poster.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/58d8aa807cc486f14ce4eb7475d9e08e.webm?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/58d8aa807cc486f14ce4eb7475d9e08e.mp4?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/94ea4d9b9cc17131d70e1e30a32054e5.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过单人模式，探索Enid的故事并找回遗失的碎片，或者与朋友联手解开双人战役中的所有秘密。每个战役都有自己的关卡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/05d03e37e553a4c9075d7f272c2efc61.poster.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/05d03e37e553a4c9075d7f272c2efc61.webm?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/05d03e37e553a4c9075d7f272c2efc61.mp4?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/59b37d6049f9f81a2327597d14d9d3e3.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个战役都有4个世界可供探索，每个世界包含超过60个关卡。但挑战并不止于此，你还可以重新挑战每个关卡，以提高你的时间，成为最棒的玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/239f22dc8da9bde7beb1b8032fbd033a.poster.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/239f22dc8da9bde7beb1b8032fbd033a.webm?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/239f22dc8da9bde7beb1b8032fbd033a.mp4?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/d52ff3f0542f840315f20aa576160261.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个世界的末尾，你将面临一位强大的BOSS，每个BOSS都有独特的机制。准备好应用你在冒险过程中学到的一切，赢得这些战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/17639a24ef8ceecd533c7ddcc89d13cb.poster.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/17639a24ef8ceecd533c7ddcc89d13cb.webm?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/17639a24ef8ceecd533c7ddcc89d13cb.mp4?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/44c5dfc47f19c8a1438ea78ba5cd4452.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某些关卡中寻找隐藏的收藏品，解锁皮肤并定制你的角色。确保探索每个角落：要玩秘密关卡，你需要点亮特别的火炬……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/5be0b706813d8bc832b2c3a29f53069e.poster.avif?t=1758896081\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/5be0b706813d8bc832b2c3a29f53069e.webm?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/5be0b706813d8bc832b2c3a29f53069e.mp4?t=1758896081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
